        <div class="body">
            <p>It is highly unlikely that {{Zend_Gdata}} will be supporting the replacement APIs for {{Zend_Gdata_Gbase}}, or any other non-GData-based Google APIs.  Google's GData APIs are being phased out, and as such they are no longer officially maintaining this component (Zend_Gdata).</p>

<p>The best alternative is to use the PHP APIs provided by Google via their <a href="https://developers.google.com/">Google Developers web portal</a>.</p>

